    "English": "A series of agile, high-powered jet thrusters mounted to the rear of the rear of the Minotaur. Precise use allows the Minotaur to quickly and powerfully traverse all manner of terrain.<br><br>Press and hold <span class=\"name name-img\">JUMP</span> to activate. Limited in-flight control is possible.",
